Text: Re Enron golf ballspurchasePST Done wrote You should have received feedback from me shortly after you paid Please check your feedback and let me know if you do not have it posted and I will repost Thanks again and please leave positive feedback for me as well PL Original Message From Ron Bennett ENRON Sent Monday January PM To Love Phillip M Subject Re Enron golf ballspurchase Golf balls arrived in fine shape please leave positive feedback Ron wrote Thanks I will put the balls in the mail today PL Original Message From Ron Bennett ENRON Sent Tuesday January AM To Love Phillip M Subject Enron golf ballspurchase has been sent to paypal Send balls to Ron Bennett WarrenWalker School Windmill Parkway Henderson NV Please inform me of date and type of shipping Ron Love Phillip M wrote Congratulations on winning the auction on Ebay for the sleeve of Pinnacle Golf Balls Please let me know if you will be paying by PayPal or money ordercashiers check I will mail the balls priority mail as soon as I receive payment Thanks again and use this email address if you reply before this evening is my home email and I can not access it from work Thanks again and look forward to hearing from you soon PL This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
